c',246945,'She wanted to inspire terror wherever she went. The demons happily granted her wish.',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL),(8,1173,'c',222923,'\"Priests, hunters, slayers—to arms! The enemy approaches!\"',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL),(8,1174,'r',227072,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL),(8,1175,'c',221190,'\"The time for grief is over. The time for retribution has begun.\"',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL),(8,1176,'c',234438,'\"I can make you dance to my tune like a puppet, your very blood eager to obey.\"\n\n—Olivia Voldaren',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL),(8,1178,'m',229968,'Sometimes death comes knocking. Sometimes it tears down the walls.',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL),(8,1181,'u',237355,'Not content to nudge vases and chill drawing rooms, some geists muster spectral armies to claw at the hearts of the living.',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL),(8,1182,'u',237359,'Her mind was quite gone, yet she spoke nothing but truth.',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL),(8,1189,'r',249663,'On Innistrad, death is just a career change.',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL),(8,1192,'c',233253,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL),(8,1194,'c',220040,'\"Don\'t be afraid when you hear the wolves howl. Be afraid when you don\'t hear them at all.\"\n\n—Saint Trogen, the Slayer',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL),(8,1198,'c',235596,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL),(8,1200,'c',220393,'The crueler vampires\' idea of free-range farming.',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL),(8,1203,'u',222205,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL),(8,1204,'c',243210,'\"Is it hopeless? When wave upon wave of our dead return as mindless flesh-eaters to claw upon Thraben\'s walls? We\'re too busy cutting them down to indulge ourselves in such philosophical foppery.\"\n\n—Mikaeus, the Lunarch',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL),(8,1206,'c',221284,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL),(8,1207,'r',230787,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL),(8,1211,'c',226758,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL),(8,1212,'u',226884,'Some priests speak in whispers of the Helvault, a silver prison of unpurged evils.',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL),(8,1213,'r',226885,'He relishes the devotion of his Skirsdag puppets and their belief that it w